<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.3.2">
<l>kañcaṉuṅ kāḷiyaṉuṅ kaḷiṟummaru tumerutum</l>
<l>vañcaṉai yiṉmaṭiya vaḷarntamaṇi vaṇṇaṉmalai</l>
<l>nañcumiḻ nākameḻun taṇavinaḷir māmatiyai</l>
<l>ceñcuṭar nāvaḷaikkun tirumāliruñ cōlaiyatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain of the sapphire-hued One who grew to destroy</l>
<l rend="indent">Kaṃsa, Kāḷiya, the elephant, the Marutu trees,</l>
<l rend="indent">and the bull through deceit,</l>
<l>that is Tirumāliruñcōlai where the venom spitting serpent rises,</l>
<l rend="indent">coming near, to steal the huge, cool moon</l>
<l rend="indent"> with [its] fiery red tongue.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
